  <name>Goose</name>
  <summary>Open source AI agent for code, workflows, and automation</summary>
  <developer id="io.github.block">
    <name>Goose Contributors</name>
  </developer>
  <launchable type="desktop-id">io.github.block.Goose.desktop</launchable>
  <description>
    <p>Goose is an open source AI agent that runs on your machine as a native desktop app, CLI, and API.</p>
    <p>It works across code, research, writing, automation, and general workflows while connecting to MCP servers and multiple model providers.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Chat with an AI agent in a native desktop interface</li>
      <li>Work with local files, projects, and shell-based workflows</li>
      <li>Connect to model providers, MCP extensions, and custom recipes</li>
      <li>Use the same Goose platform that powers the CLI and API clients</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
